<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1436,1378,1589]" pageId="17" pageNumber="456">
Comments: This mangrove-breeding species is widespread in coastal areas of Southeast Asia and Australasia but recorded for the first time from 
<collectingCountry box="[707,770,1453,1477]" name="India" pageId="17" pageNumber="456">India</collectingCountry>
. It breeds in 
<taxonomicName box="[923,1176,1453,1478]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Excoecaria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="17" pageNumber="456" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="agallocha">
<emphasis box="[923,1176,1453,1478]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="456">Excoecaria agallocha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. (
<taxonomicName box="[1226,1403,1453,1477]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="17" pageNumber="456" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Euphorbiaceae</taxonomicName>
), a host plant shared with another adramine, 
<taxonomicName box="[655,940,1491,1515]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Piestometopon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="456" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="luteiceps">
<emphasis box="[655,940,1491,1515]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="456">Piestometopon luteiceps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
de Meijere (= 
<taxonomicName authority="Hardy" authorityName="Hardy" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Acinoeuphranta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="456" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zeylanica">
<emphasis box="[1131,1436,1491,1515]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="456">Acinoeuphranta zeylanica</emphasis>
Hardy
</taxonomicName>
), also widespread in Southeast Asia and recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[871,983,1528,1552]" name="Sri Lanka" pageId="17" pageNumber="456">Sri Lanka</collectingCountry>
(Hancock and Drew, 
<number box="[1237,1296,1528,1552]" pageId="17" pageNumber="456" value="2005.0">2005</number>
) but not yet known from 
<collectingCountry box="[299,362,1565,1589]" name="India" pageId="17" pageNumber="456">India</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
